body:
@IzzyHibbert thanks for posting this. In the [docs](https://uber.github.io/ludwig/user_guide/#csv-format) we suggest to escape the commas within the text with `\\,`, so first thing I would try to do that.
Let me know if this solves your problem.

Personally I prefer to be a bit more strict on the data side rather than letting things pass or being filtered out, because those could become problems down the line.
